620
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] idemo još dalje,

621
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] što je najbitnije, Isusu Hristu,

622
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] znači, to je to.

623
00:16:55,659 --> 00:16:57,360
[SPEAKER_01] Iz toga svega proizlazi sve.

624
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:57,860
[SPEAKER_01] I sad,

625
00:16:57,860 --> 00:17:01,120
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljstvo kao tako,

626
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] malo povlače sa sobom

627
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,640
[SPEAKER_01] neke pozitivne emocije i tako dalje,

628
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:08,759
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta jedan, možda jedan dubinski mir

629
00:17:08,759 --> 00:17:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] i usmjerenost jedne zajednice

630
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] koja ide naprijed kao nekakav,

631
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,119
[SPEAKER_01] evo rekli bismo, je vlak,

632
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] ide naprijed prema ostvarenju,

633
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,740
[SPEAKER_01] ide do neke stanice,

634
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je to.

635
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, redovnička zajednica je puno zaista

636
00:17:23,539 --> 00:17:25,619
[SPEAKER_01] i mi smo, s jedne strane,

637
00:17:25,619 --> 00:17:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] puno toga radimo sličnoga,

638
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] a s druge strane smo opet i različiti,

639
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:36,200
[SPEAKER_01] možda ona razlika između klauzurnih redovnica

640
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,740
[SPEAKER_01] i aktivnih, to je ta temeljna stvar,

641
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] a koliko vidim u svom djelovanju,

642
00:17:41,380 --> 00:17:42,299
[SPEAKER_01] evo kao redovnice,

643
00:17:42,299 --> 00:17:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] koje je, evo, dosta često dolazi

644
00:17:44,539 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] do različitih slojeva društva,

645
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,180
[SPEAKER_01] možda,

646
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] možda još uvijek

647
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:51,339
[SPEAKER_01] smo prisutne kao,

648
00:17:51,339 --> 00:17:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] kao neke žene,

649
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:57,140
[SPEAKER_01] koje su na određeni način odjevene,

650
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] i možda,

651
00:17:59,220 --> 00:18:00,839
[SPEAKER_01] možda onako nekako u svojim,

652
00:18:00,839 --> 00:18:03,640
[SPEAKER_01] i po načinu života,

653
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] i po, ne znam čemu drugom,

654
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] a po promišanju,

655
00:18:06,319 --> 00:18:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] bi možda bile izvan ovoga svijeta,

656
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] a mi smo i takako u ovome svijetu,

657
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] znači sa,

658
00:18:13,259 --> 00:18:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] najčešće smo s osobama,

659
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,700
[SPEAKER_01] ondje gdje oni jesu,

660
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] znači možda i u najtežim trenucima,

661
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] i možda imamo puno, puno širu sliku,

662
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] evo, na primjer, ne znam,

663
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] ljudske potrebe,

664
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] nego netko drugi,

665
00:18:26,019 --> 00:18:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] znate, tako da to je ta jedna,

666
00:18:27,519 --> 00:18:27,799
[SPEAKER_01] možda,

667
00:18:27,799 --> 00:18:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] možda je jedna stvar,

668
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:31,240
[SPEAKER_01] to možda nazovemo to predrasuda,

669
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] s druge strane,

670
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,839
[SPEAKER_01] vidim jedno veliko povjerenje,

671
00:18:33,839 --> 00:18:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] koje kao redovnica,

672
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:40,700
[SPEAKER_01] dobivam u komunikaciji sa,

673
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] evo, opet sa različitim,

674
00:18:42,099 --> 00:18:45,839
[SPEAKER_01] i osobama i organizacijama i tako dalje,

675
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:47,240
[SPEAKER_01] i baš to možda temeno povjerenje,

676
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,700
[SPEAKER_01] da ti kao redovnica,

677
00:18:48,700 --> 00:18:50,440
[SPEAKER_01] ćeš ja kao redovnica,

678
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,339
[SPEAKER_01] ipak nosim nešto drugačije,

679
00:18:52,339 --> 00:18:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] možda, evo,

680
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] taj crkva je po nama,

681
00:18:56,619 --> 00:18:58,700
[SPEAKER_01] evo, možda na drugačiji način,

682
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] prisutna u svim tim interakcijama

683
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:02,240
[SPEAKER_01] koje se događaju u našem redovitom životu,

684
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] u mom životu,

685
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,920
[SPEAKER_01] tako da možda to je jedno dodatno povjerenje,

686
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] s jedne strane,

687
00:19:05,619 --> 00:19:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] s druge strane predrasude,

688
00:19:07,019 --> 00:19:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] kao da ja možda neću razumijeti nešto,

689
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] s treće strane,

690
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:13,299
[SPEAKER_01] evo, rekla sam ono,

691
00:19:13,299 --> 00:19:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] znači, bit ćemo svi zajedno

692
00:19:14,579 --> 00:19:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] autentični i vrijedni toga,

693
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] dostojni toga povjerenja,

694
00:19:18,579 --> 00:19:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] na koncu koji Bog ima u nas,

695
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] ako budemo zaista ono što trebamo biti,

696
00:19:23,019 --> 00:19:24,160
[SPEAKER_01] znači, odaziv, odnosno,

697
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, Isus,

698
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,240
[SPEAKER_01] karizma,

699
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] ja osobno,

700
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,160
[SPEAKER_01] i to sve skupak,

701
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] kad to stavite sve zajedno,

702
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] onda možda odobivate odgovor,

703
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako da zadovoljstvo,

704
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno poziv je osoban i...

705
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] I vi ga osjećate.

706
00:19:38,319 --> 00:19:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja ga osjećam,

707
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,160
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da ga osjećam,

708
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da taj svatko od nas,

709
00:19:42,819 --> 00:19:44,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima taj jedan poziv,

710
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] i vi kao suprug,

711
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,140
[SPEAKER_01] ili tako,

712
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:46,700
[SPEAKER_01] otac,

713
00:19:46,700 --> 00:19:48,200
[SPEAKER_01] tako da uspijete,

714
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,099
[SPEAKER_01] jeste li vi zadovoljni?

715
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno.

716
00:19:50,019 --> 00:19:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

717
00:19:50,460 --> 00:19:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odazvali ste se na ono što je bilo izvorno vaše?

718
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,359
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tako da ja,

719
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:56,759
[SPEAKER_01] u sebi isto tako,

720
00:19:56,759 --> 00:19:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] ako sad nastavit ćete vi,

721
00:19:58,119 --> 00:20:01,220
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja znam da je to nešto bilo izvorno moje

722
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] i koje sam razvijala,

723
00:20:02,579 --> 00:20:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] još uveć ću razvijati do do smrti.

724
00:20:04,099 --> 00:20:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ga to razvijate na specifičan način,

725
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] služeći ljudima sa margine i potrebitima,

726
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] ali uz to također imate,

727
00:20:12,299 --> 00:20:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] i što sam zapravo,

728
00:20:13,140 --> 00:20:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] iako sam već po razgovaru s vama,

729
00:20:14,859 --> 00:20:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] iako smo već hodili razgovor tamo negdje 2019.

730
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,220
[SPEAKER_00] niste radili priču, zabitno ne.

731
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kada sam ponovno išao čititi o vama

732
00:20:21,279 --> 00:20:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] i pripremati se za ovaj naš sustred današnji,

733
00:20:23,799 --> 00:20:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] nisam znao da se bavite i povišću.

734
00:20:26,599 --> 00:20:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

735
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da ste završili povijest.

736
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam doktorirala sam povijest,

737
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] suremenu povijest,

738
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo nastavak rada,

739
00:20:34,119 --> 00:20:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] moga sam ubiti od 2017,

740
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,799
[SPEAKER_01] u stvari prije toga,

741
00:20:37,799 --> 00:20:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] deset godina prije toga,

742
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:41,660
[SPEAKER_01] počela sam baviti se

743
00:20:41,660 --> 00:20:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] povišću svoje družbe,

744
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači, a to je komunističkim razlogom,

745
00:20:46,019 --> 00:20:47,660
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam dobila jedan lijepi zadatak,

746
00:20:47,660 --> 00:20:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] a to je napisati životopis,

747
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,140
[SPEAKER_01] kako sam završila je hrvatski,

748
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] životopis sestre Žarke Ivasić,

749
00:20:52,940 --> 00:20:54,259
[SPEAKER_01] mučenice komunističkog režina.

750
00:20:54,259 --> 00:20:55,359
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam se bavila,

751
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,740
[SPEAKER_01] sam se jako puno,

752
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] evo, tim njezinim detaljima njezina života,

753
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,900
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo baš znanstveni rad praktički.

754
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:03,799
[SPEAKER_01] I u tom radu,

755
00:21:03,799 --> 00:21:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] kako sam na početku već rekla,

756
00:21:05,579 --> 00:21:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] Lika mi je bila,

757
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] budući da je ona mučenješkog smrća umrla,

758
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] stiriljena je bila u Gospiču.

759
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam se dosta bavila,

760
00:21:12,359 --> 00:21:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] evo, i tim područjima,

761
00:21:14,119 --> 00:21:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] različitim drugim područjima,

762
00:21:15,180 --> 00:21:16,660
[SPEAKER_01] koji su vezani uz njezino djelovanje.

763
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] I od tog vremena,

764
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:18,819
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

765
00:21:18,819 --> 00:21:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] to je možda prošlo deset godina,

766
00:21:20,819 --> 00:21:22,339
[SPEAKER_01] njega je izišla i tako dalje,

767
00:21:22,339 --> 00:21:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] onda sam upisala sam,

768
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] poslije diplomski studij,

769
00:21:24,900 --> 00:21:26,700
[SPEAKER_01] i nastavila sam,

770
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,940
[SPEAKER_01] proširila sam tu temu

771
00:21:27,940 --> 00:21:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] na svoju družbu,

772
00:21:29,119 --> 00:21:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] znači, na, ubiti, kontekst cijeli,

773
00:21:31,019 --> 00:21:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] znači, progoni družbe

774
00:21:32,119 --> 00:21:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] od 1945. godine do 1952.

775
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] U postu kalisnička.

776
00:21:35,039 --> 00:21:36,160
[SPEAKER_00] Opisali iz ti knjigo, je li tako?

777
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] Odnos Jugoslavijansko-komuničkog režima

778
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] prema družbi.

779
00:21:38,619 --> 00:21:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, to je Milo Serđa odkupljio i odmržio.

780
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] Baš sam htio pitati,

781
00:21:41,859 --> 00:21:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] zašto te, zašto konkretno

782
00:21:43,059 --> 00:21:44,200
[SPEAKER_00] od 1945. do 1952.

783
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,740
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što je to bilo porače

784
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] i to je bilo najintenzivnije,

785
00:21:47,059 --> 00:21:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] razdoblje najintenzivnijih progona

786
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje, tako da u tom razdoblju

787
00:21:51,119 --> 00:21:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] su stradale, mislim,

788
00:21:52,079 --> 00:21:54,160
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo represija na različitim,

789
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] evo, prvenstveno, to su ljudi

790
00:21:55,559 --> 00:21:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili osuđeni,

791
00:21:56,519 --> 00:21:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili ubijeni,

792
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] sestre, odnosno i članovi,

793
00:21:59,579 --> 00:22:00,759
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, katoličke crkve,

794
00:22:00,759 --> 00:22:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] ali postoje i drugi različiti načine

795
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] i provođenje represije nad...

796
00:22:04,599 --> 00:22:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] Možete li precizirati,

797
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] ono malo navišt,

798
00:22:06,359 --> 00:22:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] šta se to zapravo događalo

799
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] sa družbom za vreme

800
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:09,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jugoslavijanskog režima

801
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] od 45. do 50. i druge?

802
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:13,079
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, budući da je družba

803
00:22:13,079 --> 00:22:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] bila najbrojnija u razdoblju,

804
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači, od kada je došla,

805
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] pa, evo, to je možda od 39. godine,

806
00:22:17,779 --> 00:22:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] gledam drugi svjetski rat porače,

807
00:22:20,180 --> 00:22:22,759
[SPEAKER_01] znači, najbrojnija ženska redovniška družba

808
00:22:22,759 --> 00:22:24,759
[SPEAKER_01] zajednica na ovim prostorima,

809
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:26,299
[SPEAKER_01] tako da je to bilo jako...

810
00:22:26,299 --> 00:22:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] evo, njihova naša djelatnost

811
00:22:29,460 --> 00:22:31,140
[SPEAKER_01] je bila izuzetno razgranata,

812
00:22:31,140 --> 00:22:32,700
[SPEAKER_01] to znate, velike škole,

813
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:34,220
[SPEAKER_01] bolnice i tako dalje,

814
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] i ono što se dogodilo je zaista,

815
00:22:37,019 --> 00:22:38,339
[SPEAKER_01] znači, mislim,

816
00:22:38,519 --> 00:22:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] katolička crkva kao neprijatelj države

817
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] nakon 45. godine

818
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] doživila velike progone

819
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,859
[SPEAKER_01] i bilo je potrebno obezvrijediti

820
