00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Jako zanimljivo.

1468
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko otprilike imate korisnika,

1469
00:36:22,659 --> 00:36:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] koliko korisnika prođe

1470
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] kroz Depola?

1471
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš je program više od 350 godišnje.

1472
00:36:28,239 --> 00:36:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] To je to, znači,

1473
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] na različite načine.

1474
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:32,280
[SPEAKER_01] Netko će ići,

1475
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] neko će primiti uslugu prehrane,

1476
00:36:34,159 --> 00:36:34,860
[SPEAKER_01] neko će uglavnom,

1477
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:36,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali to su na različite načine.

1478
00:36:36,579 --> 00:36:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, pa što je taj broj.

1479
00:36:37,579 --> 00:36:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, više od 350.

1480
00:36:38,539 --> 00:36:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] A velik broj njih,

1481
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako sam shvatio,

1482
00:36:41,059 --> 00:36:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] prima redovitu pomoć, zapravo.

1483
00:36:43,079 --> 00:36:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] Na dnevnoj bazi.

1484
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, tako je.

1485
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno.

1486
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko imate korisnika

1487
00:36:47,039 --> 00:36:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] kući i utočišta u rijeci dnevno, da?

1488
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dnevno, pa ja bih rekla

1489
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] maksimalno 70.

1490
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bilo to 70.

1491
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] I kako izgleda život u kući i utočišta?

1492
00:36:54,539 --> 00:36:57,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, najbolji način...

1493
00:36:57,019 --> 00:36:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nije tamo zaprespavati,

1494
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sad dnevni poravak

1495
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] bez kućnika.

1496
00:37:00,599 --> 00:37:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, mi imamo praktički,

1497
00:37:02,039 --> 00:37:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja gledam, imamo sve što vama treba

1498
00:37:04,099 --> 00:37:05,639
[SPEAKER_01] u vašoj kući, vašem domu,

1499
00:37:05,639 --> 00:37:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] izuzev kreveta, odnosno izuzev spavalja.

1500
00:37:08,019 --> 00:37:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ali dobro, imamo 12 sati sigurnosti,

1501
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:12,820
[SPEAKER_01] 12 sati mogućnosti da čovjek bude kod nas

1502
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] i odspava barem preko dana,

1503
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] da beskućnik bude kod nas

1504
00:37:15,579 --> 00:37:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] i pa odspava barem preko dana.

1505
00:37:16,639 --> 00:37:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je puno.

1506
00:37:17,539 --> 00:37:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jedna utočište sigurnost

1507
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] u tih 12 sati, to je nešto što je stvarno,

1508
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:24,099
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je to dosta važno njima svima.

1509
00:37:24,099 --> 00:37:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali više od toga,

1510
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] te činjenice da imamo kuću,

1511
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] da imamo jednu zgrađevinu,

1512
00:37:29,679 --> 00:37:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] imamo osobe, znači to ima čovike,

1513
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] volonter, djelatnik,

1514
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo svi svaki dan za njih.

1515
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,599
[SPEAKER_01] I ta činjenica da možeš dostati otvorena vrata

1516
00:37:39,599 --> 00:37:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] i da zaista možeš doći,

1517
00:37:40,659 --> 00:37:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] da netko će biti tu za tebe.

1518
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] I to je, mislim da nekako...

1519
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] Netko će ponuditi hranu,

1520
00:37:46,300 --> 00:37:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] netko će ponuditi...

1521
00:37:46,559 --> 00:37:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] Netko će učiniti što god.

1522
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da imate i...

1523
00:37:49,340 --> 00:37:51,639
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo duhovnu pomoć, psihološku pomoć,

1524
00:37:51,639 --> 00:37:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] imamo higijeno, hranu,

1525
00:37:53,099 --> 00:37:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] znači to su spada, mi to kažemo, temene usluge,

1526
00:37:55,340 --> 00:37:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] hrana, higijena, zdravlje,

1527
00:37:56,659 --> 00:37:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] onda imamo specializirane usluge,

1528
00:37:58,579 --> 00:38:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] rad sa uvisnicima o alkoholu,

1529
00:38:00,159 --> 00:38:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] zatvorenicima, bivših zatvorenicima,

1530
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] što je vašem društveno poduzetništvo,

1531
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] mogućnost radne aktivacije i zapošljavanja.

1532
00:38:08,239 --> 00:38:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto što je...

1533
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kad gledam Depol,

1534
00:38:10,139 --> 00:38:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] mi sebe zovemo da smo obite Depol,

1535
00:38:12,460 --> 00:38:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] a to znači da na svakom mjestu

1536
00:38:16,539 --> 00:38:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] su nam i korisnici, djelatnici i volonteri.

1537
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači kad gledate naš uvijek,

1538
00:38:19,619 --> 00:38:21,320
[SPEAKER_01] da navedim primjer kuhinje,

1539
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] u kuhinji je sad, evo u ovom trenutku,

1540
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:24,780
[SPEAKER_01] kad se kuha ručak,

1541
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] imate volontera sigurno,

1542
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] imate osobe koji su u probaci,

1543
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] imate naše korisnike,

1544
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:33,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji su se uključili u neke pomoćne poslovi,

1545
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] imate djelatnike, u ih smo svi.

1546
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da što god radimo,

1547
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek je ta jedna dinamika

1548
00:38:38,019 --> 00:38:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] koja je na koncu ljekovita,

1549
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer jedne druge liječimo,

1550
00:38:41,420 --> 00:38:43,719
[SPEAKER_01] to ne ide pomoć uvijek od mene

1551
00:38:43,719 --> 00:38:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] prema čovjeku koji je kao slabiji,

1552
00:38:45,599 --> 00:38:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] znači koji je u potribi.

1553
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pomoć je uvijek uzajamna

1554
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da to je ta jedna dinamika

1555
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] međusobne promjene na dobro,

1556
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] to je nešto što je stvarno nešto

1557
00:38:56,739 --> 00:38:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] što je jako, jako važno

1558
00:38:57,739 --> 00:38:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] i nama je to, mislim da je to nešto

1559
00:38:59,059 --> 00:39:00,340
[SPEAKER_01] što je naša osobitost,

1560
00:39:00,340 --> 00:39:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno karakteristika.

1561
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] Imate i vrti, o tako?

1562
00:39:03,019 --> 00:39:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] To su programe društveno poduzetništvo,

1563
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] znači to, kada kažem,

1564
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] to imamo vrt beskućnika

1565
00:39:08,099 --> 00:39:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] koji je rasadnik,

1566
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] gdje imamo, proizvodimo,

1567
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,860
[SPEAKER_01] uzgajamo sadnice različite obilja,

1568
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] gnojeva različita,

1569
00:39:14,679 --> 00:39:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] to su ekološka gnojeva,

1570
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:18,119
[SPEAKER_01] glisnjak, tako to je baš,

1571
00:39:18,119 --> 00:39:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] ne razumijem se puno to,

1572
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali uvijek znam to što je.

1573
00:39:20,659 --> 00:39:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] Imavo i naš pogon,

1574
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:25,199
[SPEAKER_01] zovemo ga kruhsatog vinka,

1575
00:39:25,199 --> 00:39:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] proizvodni pogon,

1576
00:39:26,219 --> 00:39:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se proizvodi različite kolači,

1577
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] onda krutoni,

1578
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] to su one prebećene kockice kruha,

1579
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,820
[SPEAKER_01] dehidrati,

1580
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,860
[SPEAKER_01] tako da to je jedan baš izdvojeni pogon.

1581
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] To prodajete te proizvode?

1582
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa prodajemo, da, tako je prodajemo zaista.

1583
00:39:39,179 --> 00:39:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] I gdje ih ljubi mogu nabaviti?

1584
00:39:40,139 --> 00:39:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mogu nabaviti,

1585
00:39:41,579 --> 00:39:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] imamo svake nedjelje,

1586
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] imamo, znači, na župama,

1587
00:39:44,619 --> 00:39:46,739
[SPEAKER_01] riješkim župama i čak istra i lika,

1588
00:39:46,739 --> 00:39:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] nekako smo počeli se širiti,

1589
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] to su nedeljne prodeje,

1590
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] a isto tako,

1591
00:39:50,079 --> 00:39:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako neko želi naručiti kolača

1592
00:39:52,579 --> 00:39:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] ili bilo što drugo,

1593
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] javi nam se telefon,

1594
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] nekako to izdefiniramo,

1595
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] pa zaista može se i naručivati

1596
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] preko naše stranice,

1597
00:39:58,159 --> 00:39:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] naše kontakta i tako da.

1598
00:39:59,619 --> 00:40:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] I isto tako, da,

1599
00:40:00,980 --> 00:40:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] imamo neke suradnike

1600
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] koje se nalaze,

1601
00:40:02,699 --> 00:40:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] čak i u Zagrebu,

1602
00:40:04,380 --> 00:40:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] suradničke koje naše proizvode

1603
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] žele distribuirati,

1604
00:40:08,300 --> 00:40:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] tako da na nekim mjestima

1605
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] se može i naći.

1606
00:40:10,159 --> 00:40:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] To sam zapravo je reći,

1607
00:40:11,239 --> 00:40:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste i voditeljica kuća u toči.

1608
00:40:12,599 --> 00:40:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam, jesam.

1609
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimljivo, zanimljivo.

1610
00:40:15,420 --> 00:40:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo sam mi se postavljeno,

1611
00:40:16,659 --> 00:40:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo imam dva pitanja.

1612
00:40:18,579 --> 00:40:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jedno je,

1613
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] jasno se znao susret s time

1614
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] i u svom osobnom životu

1615
00:40:25,260 --> 00:40:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] i u životu drugih ljudi,

1616
00:40:26,719 --> 00:40:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] a i slušajući jednostavno,

1617
00:40:29,179 --> 00:40:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] čitajući o stvarnostima u crkvi,

1618
00:40:32,699 --> 00:40:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] slušajući ljude kako govore

1619
00:40:34,739 --> 00:40:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] o nekakvim drugim primjerima

1620
00:40:36,239 --> 00:40:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] i o svojim životima,

1621
00:40:37,139 --> 00:40:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju kraja i gledajući svijet

1622
00:40:39,980 --> 00:40:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] i crkvu kako se ponaša,

1623
00:40:41,039 --> 00:40:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo na zapadu,

1624
00:40:42,019 --> 00:40:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] zna se dogodi taj napasnost

1625
00:40:44,539 --> 00:40:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] da zbog pojačanog aktivizma

1626
00:40:47,619 --> 00:40:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] zapustimo ono duhovno.

1627
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da li se vi susrećate s tomu pasnošću

1628
00:40:52,199 --> 00:40:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] i kako se nosite

1629
00:40:54,119 --> 00:40:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] sa tim izazovima pomiriti

1630
00:40:55,739 --> 00:40:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] akciju i kontemplaciju?

1631
00:40:58,300 --> 00:41:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, uvezi ovog pitanja,

1632
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je,

1633
00:41:02,559 --> 00:41:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] volim isticati suradnju,

1634
00:41:05,599 --> 00:41:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] našu suradnju,

1635
00:41:06,599 --> 00:41:07,719
[SPEAKER_01] Depol Hrvatske,

1636
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] či Vinkovske organizacije,

1637
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] sa zajednicom Monitva i Riječi

1638
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] i Centrum za hagioterapiju.

1639
00:41:13,159 --> 00:41:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] i to je ta jedna naša,

1640
00:41:15,039 --> 00:41:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] kao dva krila,

1641
00:41:16,219 --> 00:41:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] reklo bi se, znate,

1642
00:41:17,039 --> 00:41:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje,

1643
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] iz te suradnje naše,

1644
00:41:21,739 --> 00:41:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno proizlazi

1645
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] iz rada,

1646
00:41:25,559 --> 00:41:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] individualnog rada

1647
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] s korisnicima,

1648
00:41:28,199 --> 00:41:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] s djelatnicima,

1649
00:41:29,219 --> 00:41:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] s volonterima,

1650
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] proizlazi to

1651
00:41:33,059 --> 00:41:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] da smo se jednostavno,

1652
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] sustavno smo,

1653
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,599
[SPEAKER_01] odlučili smo se

1654
00:41:36,599 --> 00:41:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] usmjeravati na bitno.

1655
00:41:38,019 --> 00:41:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Odlučili smo se usmjeravati na bitno.

1656
00:41:40,659 --> 00:41:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] to znači ne zapostavljati svoje temelje.

1657
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ići prema,

1658
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:47,099
[SPEAKER_01] evo što ste rekli,

1659
00:41:47,099 --> 00:41:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] pretiranom aktivizmu

1660
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] i ne se zavaravati time.

1661
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,820
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1662
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] ti programe koje mi provodimo

1663
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] su biti

1664
00:41:56,539 --> 00:41:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] vezani i uz

1665
00:41:59,199 --> 00:42:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] rad sa djelatnicima,

1666
